text: Aleksandr Volkov (born 28 March 1978) is a Russian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1998 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Russia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:People from Kirov, Kirov Oblast
title: Aleksandr Volkov (ski jumper)
